%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Program Manager
participant UI as Legal UI
participant BFF as Legal BFF
participant ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
participant SERVICE as Legal Validation Service
participant OPENTEXT as MSIL OpenText DMS
participant PRIMARYDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}
participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}
participant NS as Notification Service

PM ->> UI: Create Legal Validation Request
UI ->> BFF: Submit request details and document copy
BFF ->> ORCH: startLegalRequestSubmission()

ORCH ->> SERVICE: validateRequestByDocumentType()
alt Validation Failed
    SERVICE -->> ORCH: Mandatory field errors
    ORCH -->> BFF: Return validation errors
    BFF -->> UI: Show inline errors
else Validation Passed
    ORCH ->> OPENTEXT: Store legal review document copy
    OPENTEXT -->> ORCH: document_id and metadata

    ORCH ->> SERVICE: createAndSubmitLegalRequest()
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT legal_validation_request(status='Open')
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT legal_request_document
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT legal_request_comment
    SERVICE ->> PRIMARYDB: INSERT legal_request_audit(action='SUBMIT_LEGAL_REQUEST')

    ORCH ->> KAFKA: Publish LegalRequestSubmitted
    KAFKA ->> NS: Notify Legal Team

    ORCH -->> BFF: Submit success
    BFF -->> UI: Show request submitted with status Open
end